{"tid":770162,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港股已步入熊市　投資者宜先離場觀望","createTime":"2018-08-07T00:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T01:24:02.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e9bdc7f7da84fdea37d87e52af2e9c2b3ed2bdf6","tid":770162,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T00:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180803/photo/bkn-20180803200444791-0803_00842_001_01b.jpg?20180803215433\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180803%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180803200444791-0803_00842_001_01b.jpg%3F20180803215433&h=dacbc9a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國泛海證劵投資部副總裁潘彥銘Thomas<br />\n<br />\n今集《講股半分鐘》由中國泛海證劵投資部副總裁潘彥銘Thomas為我們講股。他指受內地政治局會議訊息影響，港股被打入熊市，加上貿易戰及人民幣貶值等因素，建議投資者宜先離場觀望。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，政治局會議釋放訊息猛烈，中央強調去槓桿力度不變、而且會持續嚴控房市，不讓樓價繼續上漲，令房市快速冷卻，經濟增長力度受到抑制，導致近期股市愈跌愈有。<br />\n<br />\n若投資者仍想入市，他建議應持一種中長線坐貨心態，可選擇一些高確定性及高增長的好股份，例如藥業股中的藥明生物(02269)、中國生物製藥(01177)以及石藥集團(01093)等等，可待股價回調5%至10%再吸納，料半年以上回報可以相當理想。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180803/bkn-20180803200444791-0803_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180803%2Fbkn-20180803200444791-0803_00842_001.html&d=8pQux4UZmuDDUh%2BBBDQEejA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=bee41cc2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180803/bkn-20180803200444791-0803_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bc3477bdf2acd99394fd294f1f1604858eded66b","tid":770162,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T00:09:28.000Z","msg":"推藥股咁過癮？"},{"pid":"5c8e1a10a6f6fbca41770cd835c72d5e3a01e23b","tid":770162,"uid":17496,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T00:22:41.000Z","msg":"呢啲仆街害呀婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b427e1fc02b991c7faa9c062cf12cbed9fa9704","tid":770162,"uid":43842,"like":5,"dislike